  T    (temperature) normalised to Tnorm [eV]
  B    (magnetic field) normalised to Bnorm [eV]

  t    (time) normalised using ion cyclotron frequency Omega_ci [1/s]
  Vi   (velocity) normalised to sound speed Cs [m/s]
